1
00:00:09.880 --> 00:00:13.580
<i>The planned route of the torch relay for the 2008 Beijing Olympic Games</i>

2
00:00:13.580 --> 00:00:16.350
<i> - was officially released in April. 
 - That's right. </i>

3
00:00:16.350 --> 00:00:21.720
<i>Currently, preparations for the torch relay are in full swing. </i>

4
00:00:21.720 --> 00:00:24.600
<i>As far as we know, the torch relay of the Beijing Olympic Games</i>

5
00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:27.270
<i>will manifest the concept of green Olympics.</i>

6
00:00:27.270 --> 00:00:29.940
<i>Environmental awareness will run throughout the whole relay.</i>

7
00:00:29.940 --> 00:00:32.350
<i>The Beijing Organizing Committees of the Olympic Games</i>

8
00:00:32.350 --> 00:00:34.110
<i>have formulated environmental standards of conduct for all people,</i>

9
00:00:34.110 --> 00:00:37.580
<i>note that it's all people participating in the Olympic torch relay,</i>

10
00:00:37.580 --> 00:00:40.440
<i> - including torch bearers. 
 - Exactly. </i>

11
00:00:40.440 --> 00:00:44.540
<i>It seems that our environmental awareness...</i>

12
00:00:44.540 --> 00:00:48.830
<i>Yes. We've learned from the environmental promotion</i>

13
00:00:48.830 --> 00:00:52.060
<i>that the BOCOG requires all people participating in the torch relay</i>

14
00:00:52.060 --> 00:00:55.790
<i>not to use disposable foam tableware, or wooden chopsticks.</i>

15
00:00:55.790 --> 00:00:59.900
<i>They also suggest that we should actively reduce the use of disposable towels, etc.</i>

16
00:00:59.900 --> 00:01:03.310
<i>They particularly encourage people to take buses, 
 - That's right.</i>

17
00:01:03.310 --> 00:01:05.730
<i>to reduce energy consumption and vehicle emissions.</i>

18
00:01:05.730 --> 00:01:07.280
<i>Exactly.</i>

19
00:01:19.430 --> 00:01:21.570
- I'm home. 
 - Finally.

20
00:01:21.570 --> 00:01:23.740
Your daughter has been waiting for you all night.

21
00:01:23.740 --> 00:01:25.300
Doudou, Dad is home.

22
00:01:25.300 --> 00:01:26.780
Your rescuer has come.

23
00:01:26.780 --> 00:01:28.250
What's up?

24
00:01:29.040 --> 00:01:33.350
After you gave the speech at her school, she became interested in physics.

25
00:01:33.350 --> 00:01:35.610
Look, she's doing an experiment.

26
00:01:45.150 --> 00:01:48.920
Doudou, what experiment needs so many eggs?

27
00:01:48.920 --> 00:01:55.210
The teacher asked us to put the egg into the bottle intact.

28
00:01:55.210 --> 00:01:59.840
For the experiment, Doudou has already eaten several eggs tonight.

29
00:02:03.250 --> 00:02:05.200
Are you upset?

30
00:02:07.350 --> 00:02:10.970
The bottle is small and the egg is big.

31
00:02:10.970 --> 00:02:13.060
It can't be pushed in.

32
00:02:14.500 --> 00:02:16.020
Dad will figure out a way.

33
00:02:16.020 --> 00:02:18.620
Let's see if I can help you, okay?

34
00:02:18.620 --> 00:02:20.700
Here, hold the egg.

35
00:02:35.810 --> 00:02:37.500
Doudou, hold the egg.

36
00:02:37.500 --> 00:02:40.930
When I tell you to release it, put it at the mouth of the bottle,

37
00:02:40.930 --> 00:02:42.000
okay?

38
00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:43.940
Get ready.

39
00:02:43.940 --> 00:02:46.360
Three, two, one.

40
00:02:54.620 --> 00:02:56.080
Release.

41
00:03:02.900 --> 00:03:05.120
Mom, Mom, come here!

42
00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:06.100
Coming.

43
00:03:06.100 --> 00:03:09.180
Look. The egg went in on its own.

44
00:03:09.180 --> 00:03:11.680
Wow. It really did.

45
00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:13.360
Amazing!

46
00:03:13.360 --> 00:03:16.210
Dad, can you tell me why?

47
00:03:16.210 --> 00:03:17.740
Let me tell you.

48
00:03:17.740 --> 00:03:21.910
There are many tiny molecules both in the bottle and outside of it.

49
00:03:21.910 --> 00:03:25.160
The fire Dad lit burned some of the molecules out.

50
00:03:25.160 --> 00:03:29.740
So there was more space inside, and the tiny molecules outside were impatient to get in.

51
00:03:29.740 --> 00:03:32.480
So they pushed the egg in.

52
00:03:32.480 --> 00:03:36.720
Physics is amazing, just like magic.

53
00:03:36.720 --> 00:03:39.660
Physics isn't magic.

